- tsconfig strict; no implicit any; isolatedModules.
- Explicit props/state interfaces; avoid type assertions.
- Prefer discriminated unions/enums for statuses/state machines.
- Typed API client + response types; validate at boundaries if needed.
- Use readonly where applicable; avoid mutable shared state.
- No ambient types without justification; keep types close to usage.

